Description_lang: You exploit the enemy target's weakest point, instantly dealing damage equal to $s4% of your maximum health to $?s322113[creatures if they have less health than you.][them.Only usable on creatures that have less health than you]$?s322113[ Deals damage equal to $s3% of your maximum health against players and stronger creatures under $s2% health.][.]$?s325095[Reduces delayed Stagger damage by $325095s1% of damage dealt.]?s325215[Spawns $325215s1 Chi Spheres, granting 1 Chi when you walk through them.]?s344360[Increases the Monk's Physical damage by $344361s1% for $344361d.][]

description_blz.en_US:
You exploit the enemy target's weakest point, instantly dealing damage equal to 100% of your maximum health to them.

Only usable on creatures that have less health than you.
description_blz.es_MX:
Aprovechas el punto más débil del objetivo enemigo e instantáneamente infliges daño equivalente a un 100% de tu salud máxima al objetivo.

Solo puede usarse en criaturas con menos salud que tú.
description_blz.pt_BR:
Você explora o ponto mais fraco do inimigo, causando dano equivalente a 100% do seu máximo de pontos de vida instantaneamente a ele.

Só pode ser usado em inimigos com menos pontos de vida que você.
description_blz.de_DE:
Ihr nutzt die größte Schwachstelle des gegnerischen Ziels aus und fügt ihm sofort Schaden in Höhe von 100% Eurer maximalen Gesundheit zu.

Kann nur gegen Kreaturen eingesetzt werden, die weniger Gesundheit haben als Ihr.
description_blz.en_GB:
You exploit the enemy target's weakest point, instantly dealing damage equal to 100% of your maximum health to them.

Only usable on creatures that have less health than you.
description_blz.es_ES:
Explotas el punto débil del objetivo para infligir al instante una cantidad de daño equivalente a un 100% de tu salud máxima al objetivo.

Solo se puede usar con criaturas que tengan menos salud que tú.
description_blz.fr_FR:
Vous exploitez le point faible de la cible et lui infligez immédiatement un montant de dégâts égal à 100 % de votre maximum de points de vie .

Utilisable uniquement contre les créatures qui ont moins de vie que vous.
description_blz.it_IT:
Sfrutta il punto più debole del bersaglio nemico, infliggendo istantaneamente danni pari al 100% della tua salute massima al bersaglio.

Utilizzabile solo su creature che hanno meno salute di te.
description_blz.ru_RU:
Вы находите слабое место противника и мгновенно наносите урон в объеме 100% вашего максимального запаса здоровья.

Можно применять только к целям, у которых осталось меньше здоровья, чем у вас.
description_blz.ko_KR:
적 대상의 가장 취약한 약점을 노려 자신의 최대 생명력의 100%에 해당하는 피해를 입힙니다. 

자신보다 생명력이 낮은 생명체에게만 사용할 수 있습니다.
description_blz.zh_TW:
你攻擊敵方目標最薄弱的點，立刻造成相當於你生命力上限100%的傷害。

只能對生命力低於你的生物使用。
description_blz.zh_CN:
你看破敌方目标的死穴，立即对目标造成相当于你的最大生命值100%的伤害。

只可以对生命值比你低的敌人使用。
